726940f-a.title: Queens: Jackson Avenue - 43rd Avenue
726940f-a.text:
(1)
Jackson Avenue, west side, north from 43rd Avenue to
Oueens Boulevard (in the background).
P. L. Sperr  January 8, 1937
(2)
The buildings shown in the foreground in view 1, which
extend to Dutch Kills Street.
P. L. Sperr  September 5, 1940
